 ////////
 MongoDb
 /////
 >>>>>>>local<<<<<<<

 #Window
 > download mongodb server (https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community)
 > In C drive
    > create folder by the name of data
    > inside data create folder by the name of db 
 > c:\data\db

 > open 1st cmd 
    > go inside c:\programfile/mongodb/server/4.3/bin
    > mongod (this will start mongodb server on port 27017)

 > mongo cmd(console)
    > go inside c:\programfile\mongodb\server\4.3\bin
    > mongo (to test query)

#Mac
   > download mongodb server (https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community)
   > on root ~/data/db folder
   > open terminal 
        > type mongod --dbpath data/db
   > open 2nd terminal 
        > type mongo
    
 cloud
  > https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas/register
  > 0.0.0.0/0


